#: src/installation/kfmon.md:1
msgid "Using Cadmus with KFMon"
msgstr ""

#: src/installation/kfmon.md:3
msgid ""
"[KFMon](https://github.com/NiLuJe/kfmon) is a launcher that starts apps when "
"you open certain icon files on your Kobo. If you already use KFMon with "
"readers like Plato or KOReader, you may run into a conflict when you install "
"Cadmus."
msgstr ""

#: src/installation/kfmon.md:8
msgid "The problem"
msgstr ""

#: src/installation/kfmon.md:10
msgid ""
"KFMon watches PNG files in the library. When Cadmus opens one of those "
"watched PNG files — for example, while showing a cover or importing a book — "
"KFMon thinks you tapped the icon and launches the matching reader. This can "
"leave you with two readers running at the same time, such as both Plato and "
"Cadmus."
msgstr ""

#: src/installation/kfmon.md:15
